he same' source\nobserved at different epochs of its lifetime, and hence very useful for an\nobservational constraint of evolutionary models of the source dynamics, (iii)\nin some cases a slow acceleration of the average expansion speed of the cocoon\nalong the jet axis seems to be present.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2002 15:41:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
